Description: Installation
        ============
        
        ::
        
            [instance]
            ...
            eggs =
                ...
                edw.logger
            zcml =
                ...
                edw.logger
        
        
        Introduction
        ============
        
        This package creates a new `edw.logger` log facility that logs to
        INFO and ERROR the following events:
        
        * Viewed pages;
        * Added/created content;
        * Copied/moved/deleted content;
        * ZODB commits;
        * Raised errors.
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
